PRIVACY POLICY — FANCY TEXT

Last updated: June 2, 2026

This Privacy Policy explains how the "Fancy Text" mobile application
("the App", "we", "us", "our") handles your information. By using the App,
you agree to the practices described below.

SUMMARY
Fancy Text is a fully offline app. We do NOT collect, store on servers,
transmit, sell, or share any personal data. The App requests no internet
access, shows no ads, and uses no analytics or tracking of any kind.

INFORMATION WE COLLECT
None. The App does not collect any personal or sensitive user data. You are
not required to create an account, sign in, or provide any personal
information to use the App.

INFORMATION STORED ON YOUR DEVICE
For your convenience, the App saves the following locally on your device only,
using Android's standard on-device storage:
  • Styles you mark as favorites
  • A short list of text you have recently copied
  • The most recent text you typed into the App
This information never leaves your device, is not accessible to us or any
third party, and is permanently removed when you clear the App's data or
uninstall the App.

PERMISSIONS
The App requests no special permissions. It does not request internet,
location, contacts, camera, microphone, or storage access.

CLIPBOARD
When you tap "Copy", the App places your styled text on your device's
clipboard so you can paste it elsewhere. When you tap "Paste", the App reads
text from your clipboard to fill the input field. These actions occur entirely
on your device, only when you initiate them, and the content is never sent
to us.

SHARING TEXT
When you choose to share styled text, your device lets you pick another app
(such as a messaging or social app) to send it to. That action is controlled
by you, and any text you share is then handled by the app you select, under
that app's own privacy policy.

INTERNET AND NETWORK ACCESS
The App has no internet permission and therefore cannot — and does not — send
any data over the internet.

THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
The App contains no third-party advertising, analytics, crash-reporting, or
tracking services, and includes no third-party SDKs that collect data.

CHILDREN'S PRIVACY
The App is suitable for users of all ages. It does not collect any personal
information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.

DATA SECURITY
Because no data is collected or transmitted, there is no personal data for us
to store or secure on servers. Any information saved by the App stays on your
device and remains under your control.

CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be
posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date.
